text: Raazz Mahal (Translation :Royal Palace - Mystery Of Demon) is an Indian Hindi- language fantasy drama television series premiered on 28 November 2022 on Shemaroo Umang. Produced by Rashmi Sharma under the banner of Rashmi Sharma Telefilms, it stars Himanshu Soni, Neha Harsora and Ridheema Tiwari. == Cast == * Himanshu Soni as Adhiraj * Neha Harsora as Sunaina * Ridheema Tiwari as Chandralekha * Vaidehi Nair * Preeti Puri * Aarav Chowdhary == References == == Other websites == * * Raazz Mahal - Dakini Ka Rahasya on ShemarooMe Category:Pages with unreviewed translations Category:2022 Indian television series debuts Category:2023 Indian television series endings Category:Hindi- language television series
